aetherhaven.storyQuests.q_house_fisherman.objective.token=Take the house plot token from Reed.
aetherhaven.storyQuests.q_house_fisherman.objective.build=Stake and build the house prefab.
aetherhaven.storyQuests.q_house_fisherman.objective.assign=Assign Reed as resident on the house management block.
aetherhaven.storyQuests.q_house_fisherman.objective.talk=Find Reed and close the quest in dialogue.
